definition: Yu the Great (c. 21st century BC), mythical leader who tamed the floods/surname Yu

sentences.english: And women who are more than ninety-one percent rate caries.
sentences.chinese: 而女性患齲率則超過百分之九十一。

sentences.english: Objective To understand the dental caries status of preschool children in Bao an district ShenZhen city.
sentences.chinese: 目的瞭解深圳市寶安區學齡前兒童患齲狀況。

sentences.english: The decay must be cleaned out and the cavity filled by a dentist.
sentences.chinese: 必須由牙科醫生把齲壞清理乾淨並充填。

sentences.english: The decay is very deep, so I will use a local anesthetic before drilling.
sentences.chinese: 齲洞很深，在鑽牙前我將給您打一針麻藥。

sentences.english: Conclusion The prevention of dental caries with fluorinated bubbles is effective to the children aging from 3 to 6.
sentences.chinese: 結論氟化泡沫對3～6歲組兒童的齲病預防是有效的。

sentences.english: The service commission is 1%. So you should pay 5 RMB yuan.
sentences.chinese: 手續費按匯款額的1%收齲所以您須付5元人民幣。

sentences.english: The proteolytic phenomenon in enamel caries has been investigated from three directions.
sentences.chinese: 作者從三個方面探討牙釉質齲病變中的蛋白溶解現象。

sentences.english: I personally use it to effectively treat aphthas and caries in baby teeth.
sentences.chinese: 我個人用它來治療嬰兒牙齒的口瘡和齲病，效果顯著。

sentences.english: Objective To investigate the clinical effects of glass ionomer and fluoride varnishes in the treatment of root surface caries in senile patients.
sentences.chinese: 目的比較玻璃離子和氟化鈉修復預防根面齲的效果。

sentences.english: Conclusion Actinomyces is the dominant bacterium of dental root surface caries.
sentences.chinese: 結論支持放線菌是根面齲優勢菌。
